    <div class="text-lg text-text leading-loose space-y-5 animate-fade-up delay-1">
      <p>pm at initia. building [redacted] — shipping soon.</p>

      <p>before this: co-founded knowhere labs (terra's first nft marketplace, $30m volume). tech lead at tokenomist.ai. smart contracts at scb 10x.</p>

      <p>i build across the stack — nestjs, react, solidity. run parallel claude code sessions across three repos. built kanly to keep them from lying to each other.</p>

      <p>based in bangkok. reads stoics and wuxia between builds. golfs when the terminal closes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 space-y-4 animate-fade-up delay-2">
      <div><a href="/kanly" class="text-spice text-lg hover:underline">→ kanly</a></div>
      <div><a href="/projects" class="text-spice text-lg hover:underline">→ projects</a></div>
      <div><a href="/writing" class="text-spice text-lg hover:underline">→ writing</a></div>
